## Gateway Configuration

### Route Configuration
```bash
# Configure API routes
ansible {{ region }}_gateway -m template -a "
  src=api-routes.conf.j2
  dest=/etc/nginx/conf.d/api-routes.conf
"

# Configure rate limiting
ansible {{ region }}_gateway -m template -a "
  src=rate-limit.conf.j2
  dest=/etc/nginx/conf.d/rate-limit.conf
"
```

### Security Policies
```bash
# Configure CORS policies
ansible {{ region }}_gateway -m blockinfile -a "
  dest=/etc/nginx/conf.d/api-routes.conf
  marker='# {mark} CORS CONFIGURATION'
  block='
    add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin \"{{ cors_origin | default('*') }}\";
    add_header Access-Control-Allow-Methods \"GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, OPTIONS\";
    add_header Access-Control-Allow-Headers \"Authorization, Content-Type\";
  '
"
```

